80","tid":1563262,"uid":34297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:54:27.000Z","msg":"[多圖高清] [不廢up] 一人一文宣行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560411</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aabd2117a73a23835cf810a6fc5cb171156dca8b","tid":1563262,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:59:50.000Z","msg":"死返大灣區 ！"},{"pid":"39e9e8c1c17892b49ce27f59ff62f5a49f4c4554","tid":1563262,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:00:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">旺區兼狗竇前面搶犯？？？就算俾你搶到，去得邊呀仆街？？？！！！</span></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>為左殤台個牌為左碗飯，童星老監馮生都要做奶共狗鳥！！！<br />\n<br />\n為紀念燒死林彬而起嘅18樓C座，狗馮既係老監亦負責主要角色，啱啱居然勁做維撚狗，幫狗政Spin話831死人只係街邊八婆鳩吹出黎，又吹香港咁大城市死幾個人點會遮得到！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘩嘩嘩！！我愈聽愈以為轉左俾Mei西監製添！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>疑點1: </ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n光明正大點解要cap圖唔直接放片？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點2: </strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解Cap既所有圖都唔見畜聾打人，直播又會見到？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點3: </strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁撚簡單既事點解要封站兩日？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點4: </strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n連721都唔會4個部門一齊見記者，點解831會？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我依家信太子有無辜市民被殺害了</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一句到尾啦，係支共命令&quot;止暴制亂&quot;之下，明知一日拖一日尤其頭七都唔交出足本只會愈拖愈亂，咁都唔交你地話點解呢？？？？</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加埋依家毛EE爆料，831事件冇人死？？？<br />\n<br />\n<strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFYI，當晚現場傳第一消息：有人打死人，但唔係香港警察，你話係邊個呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？？！！！</span></span></span></strong></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5d046c3d5ece3b6c9ab8efe549e4015460150aac","tid":1563262,"uid":41608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:45:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2a6573cbe657455f2c02df3ffbbebd9dbd4553f","tid":1563262,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:46:42.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/